OL,3,CRaheem Sterling arrested on suspicion
OL,4,Cof drug driving after M3 crash
OL,6,FFormer England star Raheem Sterling
OL,7,Fhas been arrested on suspicion of
OL,8,Fdriving "whilst unfit through drugs"
OL,9,Fafter crashing his Lamborghini on the
OL,10,FM3 at 9am on Thursday, a source close
OL,11,Fto the footballer says.
OL,13,FThe source said the ex-Manchester City
OL,14,Fand Chelsea winger, who ended this
OL,15,Fseason playing for Feyenoord in the
OL,16,FNetherlands, had been suffering from
OL,17,F"immeasurable" psychological strain
OL,18,Fafter an "extremely tough couple of
OL,19,Fyears".
