OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780214795
OL,3,CRaheem Sterling arrested on suspicion
OL,4,Cof drug driving after M3 crash
OL,6,FSterling, 31, was arrested on Thursday
OL,7,Fmorning by Hampshire Constabulary
OL,8,Fwhile driving a Lamborghini on the
OL,9,Fsouthbound carriageway of the M3.
OL,11,FIn a statement, the force said: "Just
OL,12,Fbefore 9am on Thursday (May 28), we
OL,13,Freceived reports that a Lamborghini
OL,14,Fwas in collision with barriers on the
OL,15,FM3 southbound, close to the Minley
OL,16,FInterchange.
OL,18,F"No other vehicles were involved and
OL,19,Fno injuries were reported.
OL,26,@sD@aOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780214795
OL,3,CRaheem Sterling arrested on suspicion
OL,4,Cof drug driving after M3 crash
OL,6,F"The driver, a 31-year-old man from
OL,7,FBerkshire, has been arrested on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of driving a vehicle whilst
OL,9,Funfit through drugs, driving
OL,10,Fdangerously, possession of a class C
OL,11,Fdrug and failing to provide a
OL,12,Fspecimen. He has been bailed while our
OL,13,Finquiries continue."
OL,15,FConfirming Sterling's arrest, the
OL,16,Fsource said the incident "brings into
OL,17,Fthe spotlight modern treatment of
OL,18,Fplayers who are no longer 'fit for
OL,19,Fpurpose' ` disposable".
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780214795
OL,3,CRaheem Sterling arrested on suspicion
OL,4,Cof drug driving after M3 crash
OL,6,F"How a prolific English international
OL,7,Fwho has steered the England squad to
OL,8,Fsignificant heights over the last
OL,9,Fdecade has been made to feel worthless
OL,10,F` forgotten about," they said.
OL,12,F"The psychological strain that has put
OL,13,Fon him is immeasurable. Isolated. The
OL,14,Fsecond he touches a ball, being told
OL,15,Fhe's a flop and he's finished. Mocked.
OL,16,FHeckled.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@SO]tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780214795
OL,3,CRaheem Sterling arrested on suspicion
OL,4,Cof drug driving after M3 crash
OL,6,F"He moved to the Netherlands to escape
OL,7,Fand rediscover his love for the game
OL,8,Fbut the negativity followed. It's been
OL,9,Fan extremely tough couple of years for
OL,10,Fhim and this incident encompasses
OL,11,Fthat."
OL,13,FThe source said they wanted to
OL,14,Femphasise that Sterling had been
OL,15,Farrested "under suspicion", adding
OL,16,Fthere is no "proof of anything in his
OL,17,Fsystem".
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@FO]wD@JOUwD@ZO]xD@MOUyD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
