OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780214795
OL,3,CRaheem Sterling arrested on suspicion
OL,4,Cof drug driving after M3 crash
OL,6,FSterling, of Berkshire, has been
OL,7,Fbailed while inquiries continue. ITV
OL,8,FNews has contacted representatives of
OL,9,FSterling for comment.
OL,11,FThe player scored 20 goals in 82
OL,12,Fappearances for England, helping
OL,13,FGareth Southgate's side reach the 2018
OL,14,FWorld Cup semi-finals and the final of
OL,15,FEuro 2020.
OL,17,FHe came through the academy at QPR
OL,18,Fbefore joining Liverpool, where he
OL,19,Fmade his senior debut.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
