OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780214795
OL,3,CRaheem Sterling arrested on suspicion
OL,4,Cof drug driving after M3 crash
OL,6,FSterling moved to Manchester City in
OL,7,F2015 and won four Premier League
OL,8,Ftitles, five League Cups and the FA
OL,9,FCup in 2019.
OL,11,FHe left for Chelsea in 2022 but after
OL,12,Ffalling out of favour spent the 2024-
OL,13,F25 season on loan at Arsenal.
OL,15,FAfter leaving Stamford Bridge,
OL,16,FSterling joined Feyenoord on a short-
OL,17,Fterm deal in February and played eight
OL,18,Ftimes in the Dutch top flight.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
